<h2>Why People Are Buying Theragun Mini 2.0</h2>
<p>Muscle soreness and tension are universal problems, especially for active people. Full-size massage guns are bulky and expensive. The Theragun Mini became popular because it promises professional-grade percussive therapy in a pocket-sized device.</p>

<h2>What Is Theragun Mini 2.0?</h2>
<p>The Theragun Mini 2.0 is a compact percussive therapy device with three speed settings and a 12mm amplitude. Despite its small size, it delivers the same percussion depth as many full-size devices. It went viral when fitness influencers used it as a gym bag essential.</p>
<p><strong>Why it went viral:</strong> Fitness TikTok gym bag essentials videos</p>

<h2>How to Use Theragun Mini 2.0</h2>
<ol>
    <li><strong>1.</strong> Turn on the device and select one of three speed settings based on the muscle group</li>
    <li><strong>2.</strong> Apply to the target muscle with light pressure — let the device do the work</li>
    <li><strong>3.</strong> Move slowly across the muscle group, spending 15–30 seconds per area</li>
    <li><strong>4.</strong> Use for 2–3 minutes per muscle group, up to 15 minutes total per session</li>
</ol>

